{"tid":1819811,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 : 日式昆布柴魚高湯製作","createTime":"2020-01-11T06:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T14:34:20.000Z","uid":126221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2215c6cfcb08dcfd840b80e4a997c161e762aaaf","tid":1819811,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"第一次學人整日式高湯，完全失敗，請問以下步驟有無錯？<br />\n<br />\n1. 先將 6-8 片大昆布用凍水浸一晚<br />\n2. 昆布連凍水拎去煲<br />\n3. 開始有泡出，收細火，煮多三十秒，撈起昆布<br />\n4. 煲滾，熄火落柴魚花，約一分鐘後撈起。<br />\n<br />\n出黎既係高湯係近乎透明無味。請問錯在邊到呢？"},{"pid":"6151a60d309f988c2b0900920b5ddeb2bbd77feb","tid":1819811,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"材料太少"},{"pid":"ea419d6192f1c4ff43c2e52e7c2350c8bd18e936","tid":1819811,"uid":184952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"日本湯咁易煮都fail...."},{"pid":"ff701de752b6e8d2de91ec2beb5cd0b4d1f5f1dd","tid":1819811,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得係你味覺出現問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你倒一杯出黎加少少鹽再試真啲啦，加左鹽鮮味會超級明顯。"},{"pid":"5c14f14a011ab1cfe787b774126912a132066fde","tid":1819811,"uid":17159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"昆布有冇剪開"},{"pid":"29b1c9cf5358e057db460ff2a6dcb9196f717028","tid":1819811,"uid":143016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗6-8 片咁多呀"},{"pid":"722228a2e03bef26ae246ba0dfdc1c4ac2eb8ccc","tid":1819811,"uid":297835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2215c6cfcb08dcfd840b80e4a997c161e762aaaf","tid":1819811,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"第一次學人整日式高湯，完全失敗，請問以下步驟有無錯？<br />\n<br />\n1. 先將 6-8 片大昆布用凍水浸一晚<br />\n2. 昆布連凍水拎去煲<br />\n3. 開始有泡出，收細火，煮多三十秒，撈起昆布<br />\n4. 煲滾，熄火落柴魚花，約一分鐘後撈起。<br />\n<br />\n出黎既係高湯係近乎透明無味。請問錯在邊到呢